    "For instance:",
    "• Dictionary-based hybrid methods: Researchers like Xu et al.",
    "extended Chinese sentiment lexicons, integrating them with Naive Bayes (NB) (Wang et al. 2016b), while Wang and Jiang selected Chinese informative words combined with Support Vector Machine (SVM) models to improve sentiment classification accuracy (Jiang et al.",
    "2013; Wang et al. 2007).",
    "• Leveraging LDA and HowNet: Fu et al."
  ]
